Transcription.Text: Fine exhibition of sporting prints. Age of the coloured aquatint. The sporting prints by Herring and Alken are good examples of an always popular genre. Pictorial confections. The idyllic combination of figure and landscape in which these artists have specialized needs a sweet tooth of appreciation.
